=== 施無畏印 ===
{{Commons category|Abhayamudra|施无畏印}}
[[施無畏印|施無畏印]]（{{lang-sa|abhaya-mudrā}}），意为“无惧、无畏”，来自否定前缀'''a-'''加上'''bhaya'''（“害怕、恐惧、怖畏”，词根为bhī）。<ref>{{cite book|editor1-last=Buswell|editor1-first=Robert Jr.|editor1-link=Robert Buswell Jr.|title=Princeton Dictionary of Buddhism.|date=2013|publisher=Princeton University Press|location=Princeton, NJ|isbn=9780691157863|page=2}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=Monier Monier-Williams |title=A Sanskrit-English Dictionary: Etymologically and Philologically Arranged with Special Reference to Cognate Indo-European Languages |publisher=Clarendon Press |location=Oxford |page=60 |url=https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/csl-apidev/servepdf.php?dict=MW&page=60 |accessdate=2022-01-19 |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119041104/https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/csl-apidev/servepdf.php?dict=MW&page=60 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=Monier Monier-Williams |title=A Sanskrit-English Dictionary: Etymologically and Philologically Arranged with Special Reference to Cognate Indo-European Languages |publisher=Clarendon Press |location=Oxford |page=747 |url=https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/csl-apidev/servepdf.php?dict=MW&page=747 |accessdate=2022-01-19 |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119041106/https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/csl-apidev/servepdf.php?dict=MW&page=747 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
据说能使众生心安，无所畏怖，所以称为施无畏。
屈手上举于胸前，手指自然舒展，手掌向外。
这一手印表示了佛为救济众生的大慈心愿。
